* [[Faldast]];
* [[Paeregur Amaethur Donlas]], also a warrior;
* [[Rolian]];
* [[Phostral]], a notably large warrior;
* [[Lhaerand]], A mage;
* One more mage;
* A [[halfling]], not Rolian;
* One priest serving [[Tymora]]; and
* One other priest
